But I think the import bit is my InputDataConfig, specifically the ChannelName because `A channel is a named input source that training algorithms can consume`, and my channel is called "train". I am not sure how to proceed with this; is that a directory I can make myself? I assumed that this channel would be created for me. Could it possible be the permissions of my sagemaker role? It has full access to s3. I tried searching for information about aws or s3 channels but I couldn't find anything relevant.

The error includes information regarding using the distribution type "ShardedByS3" but mine is set to "FullyReplicated". Overall I'm just super confused and would really appreciate any help with this! I know the answer is probably very simple in reality but I don't feel I have enough information about the issue to determine what that answer is.

